        "description": {
            "value": "<p>The sturdy, steel head of this +3 major striking flaming shock orichalcum warhammer is shaped like a blazing comet.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span style=\"font-family: 'Pathfinder2eActions'; font-size: 1.8em; display: inline;\">R</span> command; <strong>Trigger</strong> Your attack roll with the <em>sky hammer</em> is a critical success; <strong>Effect</strong> A 6th-level arcane @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.sxQZ6yqTn0czJxVd]{Fireball} spell explodes, centered on the <em>sky hammer</em>. The spell DC is 45. You are immune to the <em>fireballâ€™s</em> effect, though your allies are not.</p>\n<hr>\n<p><span><strong>Craft Requirements</strong> Supply a casting of <em>fireball</em> (6th level), and the initial raw materials must include 12,375 gp of orichalcum.</span></p>",
